trans-unit.source: Represents a custom label for an axis.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en egendefinert etikett for en akse.

trans-unit.source: CustomLabel objects are stored in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection> class, which is exposed as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> class.
trans-unit.target: CustomLabel-objekter som er lagret i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection>klassen som er utsatt <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A>for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>klasse.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection>

trans-unit.source: Axis labels for the first label row are automatically generated unless custom labels are specified using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Akseetiketter for den første raden etiketten genereres automatisk hvis egendefinerte etiketter angis ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.CustomLabels%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify a custom label along the first label row, no axis labels will be automatically generated for the entire first row.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir en egendefinert etikett langs den første raden i etiketten, er ingen akseetiketter genereres automatisk for hele første rad.

trans-unit.source: Only custom labels may be used for the second label row.
trans-unit.target: Bare egendefinerte etiketter kan brukes for den andre raden for etiketten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.FromPosition%2A> properties determine the axis range that the label applies to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.FromPosition%2A>Egenskaper bestemmer aksen omfanget som etiketten gjelder.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.FromPosition%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>

trans-unit.source: A grid line and/or tick mark can be displayed for a custom axis label by using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.GridTicks%2A> property; this property specifies whether a custom grid line or tick mark will be drawn in the middle of the label range.
trans-unit.target: Et rutenett-og/eller aksemerkene merke kan vises for et egendefinert akseetiketten ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.GridTicks%2A>egenskapen; denne egenskapen angir om et egendefinert rutenett linje eller aksemerkene merke skal tegnes midt i området etikett.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.GridTicks%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor can be used to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren, kan brukes til å opprette og initialisere en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>

trans-unit.source: However, it is recommended that you use one of the `Add` methods in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection> class to add custom labels.
trans-unit.target: Men det anbefales at du bruker en av de `Add` metodene i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection>klassen for å legge til egendefinerte etiketter.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabelsCollection>

trans-unit.target: Initializes a new instance of the class with the specified fromPosition, toPosition, text, labelRow, and markStyle parameters.

trans-unit.source: Gets the axis that this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> object belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Henter aksen som dette <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> objektet tilhører.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to determine which <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> object belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å fastslå som <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objektet i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>objektet tilhører.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis"></xref> object that represents the axis that this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> object belongs to.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis"> </xref> objektet som representerer aksen som denne <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> objektet tilhører.

trans-unit.source: Returns a cloned label object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et klonede etikett-objekt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"></xref> object that represents a copy of the current custom label.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel"> </xref> objektet som representerer en kopi av den gjeldende egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text color of the custom label.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tekstfargen for den egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: The ForeColor property determines the text color for a custom label.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ForeColor bestemmer tekstfargen for egendefinert etikett.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value that represents the text color of a custom label.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdi som Representer tekstfargen for egendefinert etikett.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the beginning position, in axis coordinates, of the custom label.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir startplasseringen, i aksen koordinater for den egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: The FromPosition property determines the start position of the axis range the label is applied to.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen FromPosition angir startplasseringen for aksen området etiketten gjelder for.

trans-unit.source: The difference between the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A> and FromPosition properties determines where the label text will be displayed.
trans-unit.target: Forskjellen mellom verdiene i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>og FromPosition egenskaper bestemmer der etiketteksten vil bli vist.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose the X-axis has a scale that ranges from 1 to 5 (1, 2 ,3 , 4, 5).
trans-unit.target: La oss for eksempel si at x-aksen har en skala som går fra 1 til 5 (1, 2, 3, 4, 5).

trans-unit.source: In order to display a custom label just underneath the second point, you would set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A> property to 1.5 and the FromPosition property to 2.5.
trans-unit.target: For å vise en egendefinert etikett like under det andre punktet, setter du den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>egenskapen 1,5 og FromPosition-egenskapen til 2.5.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>—or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A>, depending on the axis in question—is set to a <xref:System.DateTime> value, then this FromPosition property will be displayed as a <xref:System.DateTime> value in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>– eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A>, avhengig av den aktuelle aksen – er satt til en <xref:System.DateTime>-verdi, deretter egenskapen FromPosition vises som en <xref:System.DateTime>verdien i utformeren.</xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>

trans-unit.source: This property should not be set to the same value as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen må ikke være satt til den samme verdien som den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel.ToPosition%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the beginning of the axis range that the label is applied to.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> verdi som representerer begynnelsen av aksen området som etiketten gjelder for.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a property that specifies whether custom tick marks and grid lines will be drawn in the center of the label.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en egenskap som angir om egendefinerte aksemerker og rutenett skal tegnes midt på etiketten.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.GridTickTypes"></xref> enumeration value that specifies whether custom tick marks and grid lines will be drawn in the center of the label.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.GridTickTypes"> </xref> opplistingsverdi som angir om egendefinerte aksemerker og rutenett skal tegnes midt på etiketten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the custom label image.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir egendefinerte etikettbildet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> value that represents the name of the custom label image.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> verdi som representerer navnet på egendefinert etikettbildet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a color that will be replaced with a transparent color when a custom label image is drawn.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en farge som skal erstattes med en gjennomsiktig farge når en egendefinert etikettbildet tegnes.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value which is replaced with a transparent color when a custom label image is drawn.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien som er erstattet med en gjennomsiktig farge når en egendefinert etikettbildet tegnes.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref:System.Drawing.Color.Magenta*>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref:System.Drawing.Color.Magenta*>.</xref:System.Drawing.Color.Magenta*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the label mark for a custom label.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir etikett-merke for egendefinert etikett.

trans-unit.source: This applies to labels in rows other than the first row.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjelder for etikettene i rader enn den første raden.

trans-unit.source: Label marks can only be used for the second row of labels, and are usually used to group labels together from the first row.
trans-unit.target: Etikett for kan bare brukes for den andre raden i etikettene, og brukes vanligvis til Gruppeetiketter sammen fra den første raden.

trans-unit.source: The major tick mark's line style of the relevant <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object is used for the line pattern of the mark, for example, the AxisX.MajorTickMark.LineDashStyle property.
trans-unit.target: Viktige aksemerker linjestil for den aktuelle <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objektet brukes til linje mønsteret for merket, for eksempel egenskapen AxisX.MajorTickMark.LineDashStyle.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelMarkStyle"></xref> enumeration value that determines the type of label mark, if any, to be used.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelMarkStyle"> </xref> opplistingsverdi som bestemmer hvilken type etikett merke eventuelt som skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the marker color for the custom label.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Indikatorfarge for den egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: The MarkColor property determines the color of a custom label's marker.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen MarkColor bestemmer fargen på en egendefinert etikett indikatoren.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value that represents the marker color of a custom label.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdi som Representer Indikatorfarge for egendefinert etikett.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the custom label.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på den egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: A string value that represents the text name of the item.
trans-unit.target: En strengverdi som representerer tekstnavnet på for elementet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> value that represents the text name of the custom label.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> verdi som representerer tekstnavnet på for den egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the index of the custom label row.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir indeksen i raden egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: The RowIndex property specifies the index of the row label where zero is the row label closest to the axis to ten, the further most axis label.
trans-unit.target: RowIndex-egenskapen angir indeksen for raden etiketten der null er nærmest aksen til ti, mer de fleste akseetiketten radetiketten.

trans-unit.source: Only custom labels can be used for the label rows beyond the first row.
trans-unit.target: Bare egendefinerte etiketter kan brukes for etikettradene etter den første raden.

trans-unit.source: If a custom label is used for the first row, labels for that entire axis will not be generated automatically; in this case, all labels for the first row must then be custom labels.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en egendefinert etikett brukes for den første raden, genereres etiketter for hele aksen ikke automatisk. alle etiketter for den første raden må være i dette tilfellet deretter egendefinerte etiketter.

trans-unit.source: An <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> value that specifies the index, 0 to 10, of the custom label row.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""> </xref> verdi som angir indeksen 0 til 10, radverdiene egendefinerte etiketten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the custom label text.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten for egendefinert etikett.

trans-unit.source: The Text property gets or sets the label text of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Text henter eller angir etiketteksten for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>

trans-unit.source: Note that axis labels for the first label row are generated automatically, but can be overridden using <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel> objects.
trans-unit.target: Vær oppmerksom på at akseetiketter for den første raden etiketten genereres automatisk, men kan overstyres med <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.CustomLabel>

trans-unit.source: If you specify a custom label along the first axis row, no axis labels will be automatically generated for the entire first row.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir en egendefinert etikett langs den første raden for akse, vil ingen akseetiketter genereres automatisk for hele første rad.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> value that represents the label text.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> verdi som Representer etiketteksten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the custom label tooltip text.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten for verktøytipset for egendefinert etikett.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> that represents the tooltip text.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> som representerer teksten for verktøytipset.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the starting position of the custom label, in axis coordinates.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir startplasseringen for den egendefinerte etiketten i aksen koordinater.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the starting position.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> verdi som angir startplasseringen.
